text: Come Home with Me () is a 1941 Danish drama movie directed by Benjamin Christensen. It stars Bodil Ipsen, Tudlik Johansen, Johannes Meyer, Grethe Holmer, Eigil Reimers, Mogens Wieth, Helga Frier. ==Other websites== * Category:1941 drama movies Category:Danish drama movies Category:Movies directed by Benjamin Christensen
title: Come Home with Me (movie)
